Package space.sunqian.fs.base.function.callable

package space.sunqian.fs.base.function.callable
Provides extensions for Callable.

Extension functional interfaces:

  • BooleanCallable
  • VoidCallable
  • IntCallable
  • LongCallable
  • DoubleCallable
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    BooleanCallable
    A Callable extension interface that returns boolean via BooleanCallable.callAsBoolean(), and its default behavior of BooleanCallable.call() is to call BooleanCallable.callAsBoolean() and return its result.
    DoubleCallable
    A Callable extension interface that returns double via DoubleCallable.callAsDouble(), and its default behavior of DoubleCallable.call() is to call DoubleCallable.callAsDouble() and return its result.
    IntCallable
    A Callable extension interface that returns int via IntCallable.callAsInt(), and its default behavior of IntCallable.call() is to call IntCallable.callAsInt() and return its result.
    LongCallable
    A Callable extension interface that returns long via LongCallable.callAsLong(), and its default behavior of LongCallable.call() is to call LongCallable.callAsLong() and return its result.
    VoidCallable
    This interface is a Callable like functional interface whose functional method is VoidCallable.call() -- without return value.
